flowchart TD
    A([Webhook delivery response received]) --> B{HTTP status code}
    B -- 2xx Success --> C([Mark event delivered])
    B -- 4xx except 408 or 429 --> D([Mark delivery permanently failed\nno retry])
    B -- 408 or 429 or 5xx --> E[Classify as retriable failure]
    B -- Timeout or no response --> E

    E --> F[Increment attempt counter]
    F --> G{Attempts below maximum?}
    G -- Max attempts reached --> H[Move event to dead-letter store]
    H --> I[Send alert to consumer account]
    I --> J([End retry cycle])

    G -- Retries remaining --> K[Compute backoff delay]
    K --> L[Apply jitter to backoff]
    L --> M[Schedule retry job with delay]
    M --> N([Wait for backoff period])
    N --> O[Re-attempt webhook delivery]
    O --> A
